headline: Franklin Templeton Canada Announces ETF Cash Distributions
summary: Franklin Templeton Canada today announced cash distributions for certain ETFs and ETF series of mutual funds available to Canadian investors.

headline: Virtus Investment Partners (VRTS) Misses Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Virtus (VRTS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -0.30% and -0.11%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
